png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 41}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "微软将打造 100% 原生 Win11 应用，这一动作意味着什么？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "微软 Store 和文件资源管理器合作伙伴架构师 Rudy Huyn 在社交平台确认，正在组建一支新团队负责 Windows 11 应用开发，并明确表示新应用将 100% 采用原生技术构建，不再依赖基于 Web 的组件。Huyn 发布了团队招募信息，强调产品思维和用户体验优先，不要求候选人具备 Windows 平台开发经验。有开发者询问新应用是否采用 PWA 架构，Huyn 直接否定了这一猜测，明确回应「100% 原生」。 目前微软部分所谓原生应用仍混合使用 WinUI 框架与 WebView 组件加载部分功能，而真正的原生应用应当完全基于 WinUI 构建，不通过 WebView 加载任何界面元素。告别网页套壳：微软组建新团队，为 Win11 打造 100% 原生应用"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-3dc59b978d02ce76f171b2f1fe6a73e5_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "175 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2022276317836570866"}}, "attached_info": "CkoI9KOks8mb9fJoEAMaCTExODk2Nzk5MiD2gq3OBjAAOJMBQAtyEzIwMjIyNzYzMTc4MzY1NzA4NjZ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "12_1775481168.776847", "card_id": "Q_658348543", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 115}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "985 和 211 的差距有多大？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-76ae20c2673d441d62e9ebf5129118bd_1440w.jpg?source=7e7ef6e2&needBackground=1"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "160 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/658348543"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI9KOks8mb9fJoEAMaCTEwODU3NzcwOCCClIyzBjAAOIQCQAxyCTY1ODM0ODU0M3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "13_1775481168.777087", "card_id": "Q_2024568374848496206", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 31}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "伊朗称美方营救飞行员行动或为窃取浓缩铀，这种可能性大吗？会有哪些影响？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "当地时间 4 月 6 日，伊朗外交部发言人巴加埃在当天举行的新闻发布会上回答提问时表示，美国于当地时间 5 日营救其飞行员的行动构成对伊朗领空的侵犯并存在诸多疑点。美飞行员据称所在区域位于科吉卢耶 - 博耶艾哈迈德省，而美方实施营救行动的区域却在伊朗中部，两者相距甚远。 巴加埃强调，美方的此次行动可能是一场「掩护行动」，目的是窃取浓缩铀，这种可能性不应被忽视，这次行动对美国而言是一次「灾难性丑闻」。更多资讯请下载央视新闻客户端"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-15ebb1cf4d71ade4a598144c6f477063.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "137 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2024568374848496206"}}, "attached_info": "CkkI9KOks8mb9fJoEAMaCTExOTA0NDUzOSCbsM7OBjAAODFADXITMjAyNDU2ODM3NDg0ODQ5NjIwNngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "14_1775481168.777690", "card_id": "Q_2024513171801535345", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 46}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "伊朗伊斯兰革命卫队情报机构领导人在美以袭击中身亡，这会如何影响伊反击能力与内部安全？停火谈判还有戏吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "当地时间 6 日，据伊朗方面消息，伊朗伊斯兰革命卫队情报机构的领导人赛义德·马吉德·哈德米，于当日凌晨在美以袭击中死亡。更多资讯请下载央视新闻客户端"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-51b5d348e57073894e3d469bbe554d33.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "137 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2024513171801535345"}}, "attached_info": "CkkI9KOks8mb9fJoEAMaCTExOTA0Mjc3OSCxyc3OBjAAOG1ADnITMjAyNDUxMzE3MTgwMTUzNTM0NXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "15_1775481168.778040", "card_id": "Q_13802540368", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 69}, "target": {"title_area": {"